Veuve Clicquot Demi-Sec & 19-pc Godiva Chocolates Gift Set
List.Description:
Demi-Sec, a slightly sweet style of Champagne, is at its best when served with desserts. Veuve Clicquot Demi-Sec, marked by fresh peach, nectarine and orange blossom, pairs beautifully with Godiva's assorted deep dark chocolates, smooth milks, velvety ganaches, classic truffles and pralines. Truly irresistible!

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Veuve Clicquot Demi-Sec Champagne (750 ML)
  • Godiva 19-piece Gold Ballotin Assorted Chocolates

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

List.Name: Riedel Ouverture -Set of 2 Red Wine Glasses
List.Description:
The Riedel Ouverture series are the ideal all purpose glasses for everyday use. The collection offers perfectly shaped wine glasses at competitive prices.

The Ouverture series is made from lead free crystal. The Ouverture Red Wine glass is ideally suited for the appreciation of red wines.

Each glass holds 12 3/8 oz and stands 7 3/8" high.
Sold in a boxed set of 2.

The bottle pictured in the background is for size representation only. Wine sold separately and encouraged for best enjoyment of glassware.
